priority' + Alert · ③→ Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert · ④→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"5bcf2e3c-50aa-d59e-8c1b-d905d6553c4f","name":"Note: Route by Work Type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Delegate 'standard' to Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,250],"id":"36598fc9-d7e6-20a7-b5e1-95b3483746bb","name":"Note: Delegate 'standard' to Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,760],"id":"a3483c60-610a-3d32-b245-e27674a5544d","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1270],"id":"eb8dd751-8126-ad09-4671-39fd9e2637b7","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1780],"id":"d67c740e-83b6-f633-456a-376c3f71a4b7","name":"Note: Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Routed Work\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"6e03fc2c-e694-6050-e93d-637ca69bb200","name":"Note: Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"9ebaca65-2e65-610a-eb04-e4fa37a47191","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"d5a5d423-75ae-49fd-d822-129f8e557ac8","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per lead (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"e45c9c94-dfc9-59e7-a330-0eaba2c67991","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"d1836a28-4de9-61ff-aa9d-91d5ac726828","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"aebb7998-c295-15f6-6fab-07e7e73a8efd","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"d276db7e-da16-d1e7-e0b0-f9fa7eb45933","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"4fe6eae0-1c3d-898d-10d3-0661a154e9de","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"92f38d06-9af3-4f7a-a8f6-772bfb59fa24","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"e3da9422-49ee-4b8a-7ec3-ab74ff971a35","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"cb1877e1-ce13-afb4-7cf5-f553bd56d4c3","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"ec34efcc-5a3a-072a-3faa-dc522d6d7b3d","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\nmySql — `insert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Sort Leads Newest First · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 MySQL connection","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"5e78a63d-c734-e557-3528-2e123331458e","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Leads Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"529c5cbd-c4e3-459b-51b7-cd27b419d801","name":"Note: Sort Leads Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"3f55f9cc-4fb3-996d-c69d-c14f6eca1505","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,520],"id":"8b4b5776-cea8-7038-8c90-e75c2c05c95a","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (MySQL)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,520],"id":"877c25fb-cc05-2402-4cd1-5aef3c2a44b9","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (MySQL)\n\nmySql — `insert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Gmail · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 MySQL connection","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,520],"id":"9b322aa9-8130-dee4-5b7e-eb9010f2a5b8","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (MySQL)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Gmail\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,520],"id":"733e62a6-a00b-7644-7d07-ddc487a03834","name":"Note: Send Summary to Gmail"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,1540],"id":"f81eb06e-bdc1-38ae-8511-750b625d5bf8","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,1540],"id":"cca9ef68-4698-4529-8368-3fa3a1a3ebdf","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,1540],"id":"d94a8049-3c9f-d803-649d-d62152eb61a3","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Log applications with MySQL and Gmail\n\n**Pattern:** Form Intake · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nLog applications with MySQL and Gmail. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual outreach is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Lead Form Submission → Normalize Lead Payload → Route by Work Type → Delegate 'standard' to Sub-workflow → Merge Routed Work → Stamp Completion Time → Persist Run Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to form intake without manual effort\n- Anyone automating outreach in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; MySQL connection; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"3b784c8e-601d-358a-b6b6-4791e4c30bb6","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"20877b5d-a1b8-4287-8e68-f27dace96609","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-290],"id":"cb9dcba8-6bff-3758-bbff-4c142fb2445b","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your outreach process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-290],"id":"8f1a86f7-3f13-0270-a260-2f07f145c4be","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Lead Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Lead Payload","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Normalize Lead Payload":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Work Type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Work Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Delegate 'standard' to Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Delegate 'standard' to Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Routed Work":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Leads Newest First","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Leads Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (MySQL)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (MySQL)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Gmail","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Gmail":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"beae1153-f0c4-473b-90fb-82c384f97799","id":"FDX04791"}